%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20few%20times%20where%20we're%20sitting%20in%20a%20trench%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20there's%20%26quot%3Bartillery%20shells%20just%20dropping%20around%20you%20for%20hours%20on%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20you%20look%20up%2C%20and%20the%20enemy's%20on%20you.%20%26quot%3BYou%20see%20fucking%20a%20dozen%20or%20more%20Russians%20bum-rushing%20your%20trench%2C%20and%20then%20you%20got%20to%20go%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20trenches%2C%20fighting%20was%20extremely%20close%20quarters.%20He%20said%20he%20fought%20in%20Iraq%20as%20a%20contractor%20before%20experiencing%20Ukraine's%20trench%20warfare.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20very%20close%2C%20and%20honestly%2C%20it's%20more%20intense%20than%20fucking%20anything%20else%20I've%20ever%20been%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20was%20carrying%20out%20assault%20operations%2C%20the%20veteran%20said%20that%20he%20never%20had%20to%20sit%20in%20trenches%20for%20days%20on%20end%20as%20many%20others%20fighting%20for%20Ukraine%20have%20had%20to.%20%26quot%3BThank%20God%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20assaulting%20trenches%20as%20extremely%20dangerous%2C%20saying%20that%20there%20wasn't%20a%20%26quot%3Bsingle%20trench%20raiding%20mission%20where%20we%20didn't%20take%20multiple%20casualties.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20when%20Ukraine%20is%20assaulting%2C%20Russia%20has%20a%20defensive%2C%20home-field%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eadvantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20trying%20to%20work%20your%20way%20through%20a%20trench%20that%20you've%20never%20been%20in%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20%26quot%3Byou're%20basically%20trying%20to%20take%20the%20home%20of%20another%20individual%20who's%20lived%20there%20for%20days%2C%20weeks%2C%20months%20at%20this%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quo