20tight%20parking%20lots%2C%20the%20truck%20proved%20to%20be%20fast%20and%20fun%2C%20albeit%20ridiculously%20weird-looking.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20all%20the%20standard%20Tesla%20features%2C%20like%20a%20huge%20screen%20for%20controlling%20almost%20everything%2C%20along%20with%20some%20extras%20thrown%20in%20that%20you%20can't%20find%20on%20the%20Model%203%20and%20Model%20Y.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20found%20some%20silly%20things%20that%20Tesla%20seemed%20to%20overlook%20(like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-review-annoying-features-windshield-wheel-covers-safety-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebad%20charging%20port%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20ceiling%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehandles%20for%20entering%20and%20exiting)%2C%20but%20other%20little%20touches%20made%20the%20%24100%2C000%20truck%20feel%20luxurious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%2010%20features%20that%20impressed%20me%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20acceleration%20was%20a%20blast.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20side%20exterior%20view%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660c7c0cc442a2f676e540c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Cybertruck%20does%20not%20mess%20around%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20power.%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20acceleration%20was%20hands-down%20my%20favorite%20thing%20about%20the%20truck.%20Pop%20it%20into%20sport%20mode%20(making%20sure%20any%20passengers%20have%20their%20heads%20on%20the%20headrest)%2C%20floor%20the%20accelerator%2C%20and%20hang%20on%20tight.%20From%200%20to%2060%2C%2070%2C%2080%2C%20and%20(presumably)%20even%20more%2C%20the%20truck%20doesn't%20hesitate%20while%20gobbling%20up%20the%20road%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20regenerative%20braking%2C%20which%20isn't%20optional%2C%20took%20a%20while%20to%20get%20used%20to%20%E2%80%94%20and%20was%20particularly%20tricky%20for%20the%20first%20few%20miles%20I%20drove%20in%20the%20truck%20each%20day.%20Back%20off%20the%20accelerator%20to%20coast%20like%20you're%20used%20to%20in%20a%20traditional%20car%2C%20and%20you'll%20be%20in%20for%20a%20nauseous%20ride.%20But%20hold%20the%20pedal%20in%20place%2C%20and%20the%20truck%20cruises%20smoothly%20down%20the%20road%2C%20responding%20to%20small%20touches%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHidden%20wireless%20charging%20offered%20easy%20convenience.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20interior%20cockpit%2C%20with%20driver%20in%20seat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660b8bccc442a2f676e3e5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221150%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20wireless%20charging%20in%20the%20center%20console%20was%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20features%20of%20the%20Cybertruck.%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrow%20your%20phone%20in%20the%20slot%20next%20to%20the%20cupholder%20where%20it%20(or%20a%20key)%20needs%20to%20be%20to%20operate%20the%20truck%2C%20and%20quick%2C%20automatic%20wireless%20charging%20kicks%20in.%20It's%20a%20classy%20touch%20that%20surprised%20me%20when%20I%20used%20it%2C%20and%20I%20would%20definitely%20appreciate%20it%20if%20this%20were%20my%20own%20vehicle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20lack%20of%20door%20handles%20had%20a%20surprising%20upside.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20exterior%20of%20driver-side%20door%20showing%20side%20mirror%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660b90bd0b8e1c832cc3bc9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETouch%20the%20hidden%20button%20on%20the%20Cybertruck's%20B-Pillar%20and%20the%20door%20opens.%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20lack%20of%20traditional%20door%20handles%20was%20strange%20at%20first%2C%20I%20got%20used%20to%20it%20quickly.%20And%20when%20my%20hands%20were%20full%2C%20the%20doors%20were%20surprisingly%20simple%20to%20open.%20To%20enter%2C%20you%20press%20a%20button%20on%20the%20door%20pillar%2C%20and%20the%20door%20pops%20ajar%20%E2%80%94%20just%20enough%20to%20grab%20it%20and%20open%20it%20fully%20(or%20nudge%20or%20kick%20or%20whatever%20it%20takes%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20situation).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETesla%E2%80%99s%20nifty%20trip%20planner%20accounts%20for%20variables%20like%20the%20weather.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20central%20computer%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660b9611cd3b1779043929a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221150%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20trip%20planner%20told%20me%20what%20was%20affecting%20my%20battery%20range%2C%20including%20weather%2C%20hills%2C%20and%20using%20the%20air%20conditioner.%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20drove%20to%20a%20Supercharger%20one%20day%20and%20tested%20out%20the%20Cybertruck%20trip%20planner's%20range%20estimation.%20The%20planner%20logged%20details%20like%20hard%20acceleration%20(my%20bad)%2C%20strong%20winds%2C%20and%20air%20conditioning%20(a%20necessity%20in%20Texas)%20as%20factors%20contributing%20to%20changes%20in%20its%20assumed%20final%20charge%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20all%20was%20said%20and%20done%2C%20its%20original%20estimate%20was%20only%20a%20few%20miles%20off%20from%20what%20it%20had%20projected%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20before.%20Impressive!%20Especially%20since%20some%20other%20automakers%20have%20struggled%20with%20similar%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Cybertruck%20is%20loaded%20with%20electrical%20outlets.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20bed%20with%20the%20tailgate%20down%20and%20cover%20up%2C%20with%20suitcases%20inside.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660ba2bcc442a2f676e3fcc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20Cybertruck%20comes%20with%20handy%20outlets%20in%20the%20bed%20(like%20most%20trucks%20on%20the%20market%20today%2C%20gas%20or%20electric).%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20truck%20is%20electric%2C%20after%20all%2C%20so%20it%20should%20be%20easy%20to%20sip%20on%20some%20of%20that%20juice.%20Handy%20plugs%20around%20the%20truck's%20bed%20and%20frunk%2C%20as%20well%20as%20inside%20the%20cabin%20for%20electronic%20devices%2C%20are%20a%20common%20feature%20of%20most%20electric%20trucks%2C%20and%20the%20Cybertruck%20was%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20back%20seat%20was%20nearly%20as%20enjoyable%20as%20the%20front.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20rear%20seats%20with%20a%20passenger%20and%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660bac2cc442a2f676e4041%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20rear%20entertainment%20screen%20has%20almost%20all%20the%20functions%20of%20its%20larger%20front-seat%20main%20screen.%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20anyone%20would%20be%20mad%20about%20being%20stuck%20in%20the%20Cybertruck's%20back%20seat%20on%20a%20longer%20road%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20much%20more%20comfortable%20than%20most%20pickup%20truck%20cabs%2C%20with%20plenty%20of%20legroom%20and%20seats%20that%20aren't%20completely%20vertical.%20And%20you%20get%20a%20personal%20entertainment%20screen%20with%20games%20and%20movies%2C%20total%20climate%20control%2C%20natural%20light%20from%20the%20sunroof%2C%20and%20cupholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Cybertruck's%20adjustable%20suspension%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20enter%20and%20exit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20front%20wheel%20well%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660bc48d0b8e1c832cc3e87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Cybertruck%20automatically%20lowers%20its%20suspension%20for%20entry%20and%20exit%20when%20parked.%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20Cybertruck%20is%20bigger%20than%20it%20needs%20to%20be%2C%20but%20that's%20true%20for%2099%25%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcar-buying-tips-electric-vehicles-pricing-americans-pickups-trucks-suvs-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrucks%20on%20American%20roads%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Still%2C%20I%20appreciated%20how%20the%20truck's%20adjustable%20suspension%20lowered%20a%20few%20inches%20when%20shifted%20into%20park%20for%20an%20easier%20entry%20and%20exit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20driving%2C%20you%20can%20adjust%20this%20suspension%20higher%20or%20lower%20for%20comfort%2C%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20lockable%20glove%20box%20didn't%20require%20a%20key.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cybertruck%20interior%20showing%20the%20driver%20cockpit%2C%20steering%20wheel%2C%20and%20central%20control%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6631583a10dfcda409651395%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20need%20to%20get%20into%20your%20glove%20box%20in%20a%20hurry%2C%20this%20might%20be%20more%20of%20an%20annoyance%20than%20a%20feature.%20%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20on%20this%20truck%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20futuristic%20and%20the%20glove%20box%20is%20no%20exception.%20Even%20though%20I%20had%20full%20access%20to%20the%20truck%20with%20the%20keycard%20and%20app%20permissions%2C%20the%20Turo%20host%20was%20able%20to%20store%20things%20(what%20are%20they%20hiding%3F)%20in%20the%20glove%20box%20that%20I%20could%20not%20access%20without%20a%20PIN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20latch%20or%20lock%20also%20delivers%20a%20clean%20aesthetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20powered%20bed%20cover%20was%20easy%20to%20maneuver.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20rear%20view%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660bceed0b8e1c832cc3f1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20locking%20tonneau%20cover%20on%20the%20Cybertruck%20can%20be%20controlled%20by%20buttons%20near%20the%20bed%2C%20the%20app%2C%20or%20inside%20the%20vehicle.%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tonneau%20cover%20on%20the%20Cybertruck%20is%20just%20as%20important%20for%20its%20alien%20looks%20as%20it%20is%20for%20aerodynamics%20and%20security.%20It's%20controllable%20through%20the%20app%2C%20the%20interior%20screen%2C%20and%20buttons%20on%20the%20bed%20rails%20%E2%80%94%20and%20comes%20standard%20on%20the%20%24100%2C000%20truck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EReally%20fast%20charging%20was%20highly%20convenient.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20charges%20at%20a%20Supercharger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663395120dfb1341e901a0a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20Superchargers%20are%20known%20for%20being%20the%20best.%20But%20the%20network's%20growth%20is%20in%20question.%3Cp%3EGraham%20Rapier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20800-volt%20powertrain%20in%20Tesla's%20lineup%20charges%20impressively%20fast.%20Tesla%20has%20said%20the%20Cybertruck%20can%20travel%20up%20to%20340%20miles%20on%20a%20single%20charge%20and%20has%20promised%20to%20eventually%20release%20a%20range%20extender%2C%20or%20optional%20second%20battery%20pack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Cybertruck%20reviewers%20have%20said%20the%20truck's%20peak%20power%20tapers%20off%20quickly.%20But%20I%20didn't%20experience%20this%20in%20my%20two%20charging%20experiences%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20limit%20the%20owner%20had%20set%20to%20protect%20the%20batteries'%20long-term%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-my-favorite-features-wireless-charging-speed-range-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717753501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660b7b1d0b8e1c832cc3b36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-my-favorite-features-wireless-charging-speed-range-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Driving%20the%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20was%20a%20strange%20mix%20of%20fun%2C%20bewilderment%2C%20and%20sheer%20embarrassment.%20These%2010%20features%20impressed%20me%20the%20most.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22grapier%40businessinsider.com%20(Graham%20Rapier)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-my-favorite-features-wireless-charging-speed-range-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22United%20States%20of%20India%3A%20USA's%20giant%20slayers%20from%20various%20cities%20of%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717752884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110793652%2Cimgsize-89664.cms%22%2C%