et%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhanmigo%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20planning%20lessons%2C%20assignments%2C%20and%20tracking%20student%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20billionaire%20founder%2C%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20has%20also%20been%20outspoken%20about%20his%20belief%20that%20AI%20%26quot%3Bwill%20enhance%26quot%3B%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20despite%20worries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteachers-caught-students-cheating-chatgpt-survey-shows-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudents%20will%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20cheat%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20their%20schoolwork%20%E2%80%94%20time-pressured%20education%20professionals%20appear%20to%20be%20positive%20about%20generative%20AI%20can%20to%20help%20teachers.%20One%20major%20reason%3A%20it%20can%20help%20them%20use%20their%20hours%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20Tierra%20Harris%2C%20a%20third-grade%20teacher%20based%20in%20Texas.%20Harris%20has%20taken%20full%20advantage%20of%20generative%20AI%20services%20this%20school%20year%20to%20access%20resources%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20matter%20of%20seconds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20said%20she%20uses%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20her%20craft%20letters%20to%20parents%2C%20respond%20to%20emails%2C%20and%20even%20create%20quizzes%20based%20on%20her%20current%20lesson%20plans%20%E2%80%94%20all%20the%20parts%20of%20teaching%20that%20don't%20involve%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20room%20full%20of%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20still%20a%20way%20to%20go%20before%20AI%20is%20fully%20integrated%20into%20public%20schools%2C%20but%20Harris%2C%20who%20asked%20BI%20not%20to%20name%20her%20place%20of%20work%20as%20her%20comments%20on%20AI%20are%20personal%20and%20not%20necessarily%20the%20school%20district's%20stance%2C%20said%20that%20she's%20also%20hopeful%20that%20she%20can%20soon%20send%20AI%20resources%20to%20parents%20who%20need%20assistance%20with%20helping%20them%20with%20homework.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20principal%20has%20encouraged%20us%20to%20lean%20into%20it%20and%20not%20be%20afraid%20of%20the%20kids%20getting%20ahold%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurby%20Alexander%2C%20an%20associate%20education%20professor%20at%20Texas%20Christian%20University%2C%20said%20it's%20helped%20him%20teach%20his%20college-level%20students%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexander%20told%20BI%20that%20AI%20helps%20with%20brainstorming%20ideas%20and%20developing%20case%20studies%20%E2%80%94%20things%20he%20would've%20had%20to%20come%20up%20with%20on%20his%20own%20before%20%E2%80%94%26quot%3Bwithout%20taking%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20class%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20students%20are%20also%20learning%20from%20the%20imperfections%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20and%20sharpening%20their%20skills%20on%20how%20to%20spot%20where%20AI-generated%20content%20falls%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22501642dd-641a-4c95-8378-c0a968e531f5%5C%22%3EAI%20can%20%26quot%3Bblow%20the%20ceiling%20off%26quot%3B%20for%20students%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20there%20are%20educators%20whose%20entire%20programs%20depend%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacKenzie%20Price%20is%20an%20advocate%20for%20disrupting%20the%20traditional%20eight-hour%20school%20day.%20Price%20cofounded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F2hourlearning.com%2Fabout-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2hr%20Learning%20and%20Alpha%20School%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20program%20where%20students%20learn%20academics%20for%20two%20hours%20using%20an%20AI%20tutor%20and%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20developing%20life%20skills%20%26quot%3Blike%20leadership%20and%20financial%20literacy%20and%20public%20speaking%20and%20grit%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20assigning%20academic%20tuition%20to%20AI%20lets%20kids%20have%20a%20more%20personalized%20experience%20and%20learn%20at%20their%20own%20level%2C%20avoiding%20lagging%20behind%20their%20classmates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20literally%20raise%20the%20floor%20of%20what's%20possible%20for%20students%2C%20and%20then%20just%20blow%20the%20ceiling%20off%20and%20help%20students%20wherever%20they're%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20concerns%20about%20the%20safety%20and%20reliability%20of%20using%20AI%20in%20the%20classroom%20have%20arisen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20data%20worries%2C%20%26quot%3Beducators%20recognize%20that%20AI%20can%20automatically%20produce%20output%20that%20is%20inappropriate%20or%20wrong.%20They%20are%20wary%20that%20the%20associations%20or%20automation%20created%20by%20AI%20may%20amplify%20unwanted%20biases%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Education%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftech.ed.gov%2Ffiles%2F2023%2F05%2Fai-future-of-teaching-and-learning-report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20published%20in%20May%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20well-aware%20of%20'teachable%20moments'%20and%20pedagogical%20strategies%20that%20a%20human%20teacher%20can%20address%20but%20are%20undetected%20or%20misunderstood%20by%20AI%20models.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20opportunities%20provided%20by%20AI%2C%20including%20helping%20adapt%20resources%20to%20students'%20needs%2C%20using%20AI%20speech%20recognition%20to%20increase%20the%20support%20available%20to%20students%20with%20disabilities%2C%20and%20helping%20teachers%20%26quot%3Bextend%20the%20support%20they%20offer%20to%20individual%20students%20when%20they%20run%20out%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20some%20teachers%20worry%20%E2%80%94%20like%20many%20other%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20that%20AI%20will%20take%20their%20jobs%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20Department%20firmly%20rejects%20the%20idea%20that%20AI%20could%20replace%20teachers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20intersection%20of%20AI%20and%20education%20is%20seen%20as%20necessary%20%E2%80%94%20as%20necessary%20as%20teaching%20kids%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20if%20they%20want%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20their%20adult%20life%2C%20according%20to%202hr%20Learning%20and%20Alpha%20School's%20Price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20it's%20seen%20as%20saving%20teachers'%20time%20on%20non-teaching%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTeachers%20in%20our%20country%20are%20overworked%2C%20they're%20underpaid%2C%20and%20they're%20underappreciated.%20They've%20been%20given%20this%20impossible%20task%20of%20trying%20to%20teach%20every%20single%20student%2C%26quot%3B%20Price%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrice%20believes%20AI%20could%20be%20the%20tool%20that%20finally%20changes%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-in-the-classroom-has-some-people-worried-teachers-arent-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717752181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e7bc324102a900184c6bec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-in-the-classroom-has-some-people-worried-teachers-arent-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Big%20Tech%20wants%20people%20to%20believe%20AI%20is%20a%20good%20idea%20in%20the%20classroom.%20Turns%20out%2C%20time-pressured%20teachers%20say%20using%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20actually%20is.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-in-the-classroom-has-some-people-worried-teachers-arent-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20to%20meet%20Ukraine's%20Zelenskyy%20in%20Paris%20as%20Russia%20leans%20into%20its%20battlefield%20offensive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717752055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110793761%2Cimg