032%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20NDA%20comes%20to%20power%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20alliance%20partners%20like%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%20supremo%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party's%20(TDP)%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20will%20be%20playing%20a%20prominent%20role%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20coalition%20government%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20This%20time%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20government%20would%20be%20dependent%20on%20these%20two%20key%20allies%2C%20which%20command%2012%20and%2016%20seats%2C%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20much%20chatter%20about%20what%20the%20Modi%20government%20would%20do%20about%20its%20pre-poll%20agendas%2C%20like%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%2C%20the%20one-nation-one-election%20pitch%2C%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA).%20The%20ongoing%20debate%20over%20disputed%20temple%20sites%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20will%20also%20be%20in%20focus%2C%20as%20also%20contentious%20issues%20like%20conducting%20a%20caste%20census%20and%20reviewing%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20been%20riding%20high%20on%20the%20Hindutva%20plank%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20The%20timing%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20considered%20a%20master-stroke%2C%20but%20ironically%2C%20the%20party%20lost%20the%20Faizabad%20parliamentary%20seat%2C%20of%20which%20Ayodhya%20is%20a%20part.%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20also%20could%20not%20retain%20her%20Amethi%20seat%20despite%20being%20prominently%20visible%20in%20her%20constituency.%20People%20voted%20the%20BJP%20out%20in%20several%20seats%20in%20not%20only%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20but%20also%20other%20states%20as%20they%20prioritised%20civic%20issues%20over%20religion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20light%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20now%20have%20to%20put%20controversial%20issues%20like%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20on%20the%20back%20burner.%20Religious%20politics%20may%20have%20to%20be%20subtly%20replaced%20with%20the%20compulsions%20of%20a%20'political%20economy'.%20There%20are%20many%20'lessons'%20that%20the%20party%20will%20have%20to%20draw%20from%20this%20verdict.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20BJP%20might%20need%20to%20revisit%20its%20'basic%20structure'%20while%20simultaneously%20acceding%20to%20the%20demands%20of%20key%20coalition%20partners%20is%20going%20to%20be%20against%20its%20traditional%20working%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20himself%20had%20transitioned%20to%20a%20'Presidential%20model'%20of%20decision-making%20that%20reflected%20a%20lack%20of%20a%20consultative%20approach.%20He%20may%20now%20have%20to%20tweak%20his%20personal%20style%20to%20avoid%20rubbing%20not%20only%20the%20NDA%20alliance%20partners%20but%20even%20leaders%20within%20his%20own%20party%20the%20wrong%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECitizens%2C%20foreign%20investors%2C%20domestic%20industrialists%20and%20all%20other%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20nation's%20development%20look%20for%20political%20stability%2C%20something%20the%20country%20benefited%20from%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Quick%20decision-making%2C%20infrastructural%20development%20and%20strong%20project%20execution%20stand%20out%20as%20the%20BJP's%20achievements%20since%202014.%20There%20were%20avoidable%20situations%20-%20like%20the%20farmers'%20unrest%2C%20the%20wrestlers'%20protests%2C%20and%20the%20silence%20on%20Manipur%20-%20that%20hurt%20the%20sensibilities%20of%20the%20common%20citizens%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20party%20perhaps%20failed%20to%20gauge%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20factors%20on%20their%20pursuit%20of%20a%20straight%20third%20term%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20The%20UCC%20Debate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20boost%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20the%20JD(U)%20has%20backed%20the%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20poll'%20and%20the%20UCC%20proposals.%20But%20the%20party%20wants%20to%20engage%20all%20stakeholders%20before%20reaching%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20UCC%20has%20been%20an%20emotive%20issue%20since%20the%20beginning.%20However%2C%20the%20low%20Muslim%20vote%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20indication%20of%20the%20community's%20lack%20of%20support%20towards%20the%20issue.%20%C2%A0The%20TDP%2C%20too%2C%20would%20not%20like%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20supporting%20the%20UCC%20given%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20strong%20outreach%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20had%20assured%20them%20that%20his%20party%20would%20not%20take%20any%20decision%20that%20goes%20against%20their%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECAA%20Implementation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20was%20an%20important%20election%20promise%20in%202019.%20On%20March%2011%20this%20year%2C%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20notified%20the%20rules.%20The%20contentious%20act%20had%20faced%20numerous%20delays%20and%20continued%20criticism%20from%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20now-friendly%20JD(U).%20But%20even%20after%20re-joining%20the%20NDA%20in%20January%202024%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20clearly%20opposed%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20in%20Bihar.%20%C2%A0On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Naidu%20has%20in%20the%20past%20expressed%20support%20for%20the%20new%20rules.%20This%20may%20thus%20become%20be%20a%20tricky%20subject%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimultaneous%20Elections%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20while%20launching%20the%20BJP's%20manifesto%20on%20April%2014%2C%20reiterated%20the%20party's%20commitment%20to%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20and%20a%20UCC%2C%20but%20skipped%20any%20mention%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20for%20Citizens%20(NRC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nitish%20has%20expressed%20support%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20-%20citing%20reduced%20financial%20burden%2C%20policy%20continuity%2C%20political%20stability%20and%20logistical%20-%20the%20TDP's%20stance%20remains%20unclear%20as%20it%20had%20not%20submitted%20its%20recommendations%20on%20the%20subject%20to%20the%20Ramnath%20Kovind-led%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20Census%20%26amp%3B%20Agnipath%20Scheme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JD(U)%20has%20already%20conducted%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%2C%20and%20the%20party%20wants%20to%20now%20extend%20it%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20TDP%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20prefers%20a%20'skill%20census'%2C%20focusing%20on%20wealth%20creation%20and%20not%20subsidies.%20The%20BJP%20will%20have%20to%20do%20a%20fine%20balancing%20between%20its%20two%20partners.%20The%20JD(U)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20another%20BJP%20ally%2C%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%2C%20have%20also%20favoured%20revisiting%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20as%20there%20is%20a%20general%20feeling%20that%20the%20BJP's%20tally%20was%20in%20part%20affected%20by%20youth%20discontent%20over%20the%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoalition%20dharma%20will%20be%20a%20learning%20curve%20for%20Modi%203.0.%20In%20the%20larger%20interest%20of%20the%20country's%20continued%20development%2C%20job%20creation%20must%20take%20precedence%20over%20rhetoric.%20Identifying%20and%20grooming%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20leaders%20is%20also%20an%20idea%20that%20must%20be%20embraced.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20the%20voters%20have%20displayed%20a%20certain%20apathy%20towards%20cult%20politics%20driven%20by%20both%20the%20national%20parties.%20They%20have%20strongly%20asserted%20that%20people%20and%20their%20interests%20should%20be%20the%20sole%20objectives%20of%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20got%20the%20message%2C%20and%20now%20he%20has%20a%20chance%20to%20show%20that%20his%20credibility%20and%20the%20trust%20the%20public%20puts%20in%20him%20can't%20be%20taken%20for%20granted.%20He%2C%20his%20party%20and%20his%20allies%20are%20all%20being%20watched%20by%20the%20strongest%20pillar%20of%20India's%20proud%20democracy%20-%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717751280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fu5s968s_pm-modi_625x300_03_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffor-pm-modi-nda-3-0-will-be-about-political-balancing-5838226%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20may%20now%20have%20to%20put%20controversial%20issues%20like%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20on%20the%20back%20burner.%20Religious%20politics%20may%20have%20to%20be%20subtly%20replaced%20with%20the%20compulsions%20of%20a%20'political%20economy'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffor-pm-modi-nda-3-0-will-be-about-political-balancing-5838226%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranveer%20Singh%20pays%20heartfelt%20tribute%20to%20Sunil%20Chhetri%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717751220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110793093%2Cimgsize-53746.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singh-pays-heartfelt-tribute-as-sunil-chhetri-retires-from-international-football%2Farticleshow%2F110793045.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110793045.cms%5C%22