ctory%20here%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BPathetic%20performance.%20Winning%20and%20losing%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20But%20you%20need%20to%20fight%20till%20the%20last%20ball.%20It%20was%20a%20bad%20for%20Pakistan%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Akram%20told%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20will%20struggle%20from%20here%20onwards%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Super%20Eight%20because%20they%20have%20to%20play%20India%20(on%20June%209)%20and%20two%20more%20good%20teams%20(Ireland%20and%20Canada)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lynchpin%20of%20Pakistan's%201992%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20felt%20that%20the%20turning%20point%20of%20the%20game%20was%20USA%20taking%20early%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20stuttered%20to%2030%20for%20three%20at%20the%20end%20of%20Power%20Play%20and%20from%20thereon%20they%20struggled%20for%20momentum%20despite%20skipper%20Babar%20and%20Shadab%20Khan%20adding%2072%20runs%20for%20the%20fourth%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20turning%20point%20of%20the%20game...the%20way%20USA%20got%20early%20wickets.%20Pakistan%20had%20a%20little%20partnership%20between%20Babar%20and%20Shadab%20and%20then%20nobody%20turned%20up.%20The%20fielding%20was%20below%20average%2C%20the%20overall%20cricket%20by%20Pakistan%20was%20average%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkram%2C%20a%20master%20of%20death%20bowling%20in%20his%20playing%20days%2C%20said%20conceding%2018%20runs%20in%20the%20Super%20Over%20dashed%20Pakistan's%20hopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20playing%20against%20USA%2C%20I%20was%20confident%2C%20every%20Pakistan%20supporter%20was%20confident%20that%20they%20will%20win%20after%20the%20way%20they%20played%20in%20the%20first%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20they%20(USA)%20came%20out%20to%20chase...I%20mean%20getting%2019%20runs%20in%20the%20Super%20Over%20is%20like%20getting%2036%20runs%20in%20a%20Super%20Over.%20Well%20done%20USA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkram%20heaped%20praise%20on%20USA%20captain%20Monank%20Patel%20for%20marshalling%20his%20bowling%20resources%20and%20making%20a%20match-winning%20fifty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20moment%20of%20the%20day%20for%20me%20was%20the%20innings%20of%20USA%20captain%20Monank%20Patel%2C%20the%20way%20he%20batted...carried%20his%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20he%20used%20his%20suit%20as%20in%20he%20led%20from%20the%20front.%20Their%20fielding%20was%20spot-on%20every%20time%2C%20and%20very%20impressive%20cricket%20from%20the%20USA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717744920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Flbp3oa7g_wasim-akram_625x300_25_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fwasim-akrams-unfiltered-criticism-of-pakistans-pathetic-show-against-usa-in-t20-world-cup-5837351%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lynchpin%20of%20Pakistan's%201992%20World%20Cup%20triumph%2C%20Wasim%20Akram%20felt%20that%20the%20turning%20point%20of%20the%20game%20was%20USA%20taking%20early%20wickets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fwasim-akrams-unfiltered-criticism-of-pakistans-pathetic-show-against-usa-in-t20-world-cup-5837351%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fwasim-akrams-unfiltered-criticism-of-pakistans-pathetic-show-against-usa-in-t20-world-cup-5837351%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fwasim-akrams-unfiltered-criticism-of-pakistans-pathetic-show-against-usa-in-t20-world-cup-5837351%2Famp%2F1%22%7D