20World%20Cup%20in%20his%20youth.%20Fourteen%20years%20later%2C%20he%20shattered%20the%20dreams%20of%20Pakistan%20fans%20who%20hoped%20for%20a%20winning%20start%20ahead%20of%20their%20high-voltage%20clash%20against%20arch-rival%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20born%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20impressed%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%20with%20a%20staggering%20tally%20of%2030%20wickets%20in%20six%20games%20in%20the%20Cooch%20Behar%20Trophy%20in%202008-09.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetravalkar%20was%20also%20the%20leading%20wicket-taker%20in%20the%20Under-19%20tri-nation%20tournament%20in%20South%20Africa%20with%20eight%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20country%20brimming%20with%20potential%20and%20talent%2C%20Netravalkar%20faced%20challenges%20in%20finding%20the%20opportunities%20to%20showcase%20his%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20fairytale%20story%20began%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20he%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20represent%20a%20country%20that%20was%20on%20the%20periphery%20of%20leaving%20its%20mark%20in%20the%20world%20of%20cricket.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAgainst%20the%20mighty%20Pakistan%2C%20he%20made%20the%20Babar%20Azam%20and%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20dance%20to%20his%20tunes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20orchestrated%20Pakistan's%20downfall%20by%20leading%20the%20attack%20in%20the%20powerplay%20of%20the%20first%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20an%20early%20impression%2C%20Netravalkar%20returned%20to%20inflict%20damage%20when%20Pakistan%20were%20looking%20to%20shift%20through%20gears.%20Iftikhar%20Ahmed%20was%20the%20centre%20of%20Pakistan's%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonank%20handed%20the%20ball%20to%20Netravalkar%20to%20bowl%20the%20penultimate%20over%20and%20he%20didn't%20disappoint%20his%20skipper.%20Later%20in%20the%20Super%20Over%2C%20Netravalkar%20sealed%20USA's%20moment%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717742160000%2