20Yogesh%20Chandekar%2C%20the%20Maddock%20Films%20production%20is%20the%20fourth%20entry%20in%20the%20banner's%20slate%20of%20supernatural%20flicks%20after%20%3Ci%3EStree%2C%20Roohi%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3EBhediya%3C%2Fi%3E.%20It%20is%20no%20patch%20on%20%3Ci%3EStree%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3EBhediya%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20probably%20only%20marginally%20better%20than%20%3Ci%3ERoohi%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EStree%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3EBhediya%3C%2Fi%3E%20addressed%20themes%20that%20went%20well%20beyond%20the%20fear%20factor%20that%20the%20genre%20thrives%20on.%20The%20former%20employed%20the%20occult%20to%20highlight%20female%20empowerment%2C%20the%20latter%20used%20the%20metaphor%20of%20a%20beast%20on%20the%20prowl%20and%20championed%20the%20cause%20of%20environmental%20conservation.%20Does%20%3Ci%3EMunjya%3C%2Fi%3E%20do%20anything%20more%20than%20blending%20superficial%20humour%20and%20the%20terror%20of%20the%20dark%3F%20Not%20quite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20best%2C%20%3Ci%3EMunjya%3C%2Fi%3E%20tells%20us%20that%20dread%20gets%20the%20better%20of%20us%20because%20we%20recoil%20from%20it.%20Face%20it%20and%20resist%20it%20and%20victory%20will%20be%20yours%2C%20somebody%20tells%20Bittu%20(Abhay%20Verma)%2C%20a%20young%20man%20who%20works%20in%20his%20mother's%20beauty%20salon%20and%20yearns%20to%20break%20free%20from%20her%20apron%20strings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EMunjya%3C%2Fi%3E%20feels%20far%20longer%20than%20its%20two%20hours%20because%20the%20mumbo-jumbo%20that%20it%20foists%20upon%20us%20gives%20way%20frequently%20to%20difficult-to-digest%20twaddle.%20It%20centres%20on%20a%20battle%20between%20a%20creature%20from%20the%20nether%20world%20and%20a%20youngster%20who%20has%20nightmares%20that%20he%20cannot%20wrap%20his%20head%20around.%20People%20think%20he%20is%20on%20drugs.%20He%20has%20a%20hard%20disavowing%20them%20of%20the%20suspicion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBittu's%20mom%2C%20Pammi%20(Mona%20Singh)%2C%20is%20overprotective%20and%20baulks%20at%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20boy%20flying%20the%20coop%20in%20search%20of%20greener%20pastures%20-%20and%20a%20life%20of%20his%20own.%20But%20the%20mother%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20he%20has%20to%20reckon%20with.%20The%20child-demon%2C%20%3Ci%3EMunjya%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20more%20mischievous%20than%20malefic%2C%20pursues%20Bittu%20relentlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeventy%20years%20back%20in%20an%20idyllic%20and%20picturesque%20Konkan%20village%20by%20the%20sea%2C%20a%20teenager%20smitten%20with%20an%20older%20girl%20dies%20within%20days%20of%20his%20mundan.%20Unfulfilled%20desire%20turns%20him%20into%20a%20lovelorn%20ghoul%20who%20seeks%20human%20sacrifice%2C%20a%20ritual%20that%20he%20could%20not%20complete%20when%20he%20was%20a%20living%20and%20breathing%20boy%2C%20as%20recompense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EMunjya%3C%2Fi%3E%20follows%20Bittu%20from%20the%20forest%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Pune%20looking%20for%20Munni%2C%20the%20girl%20he%20loved%20and%20lost.%20Bittu's%20childhood%20friend%2C%20Bela%20(Sharvari%20Wagh)%2C%20who%20is%20older%20than%20him%20but%20is%20an%20object%20of%20suppressed%20affection%2C%20gets%20sucked%20unwittingly%20into%20a%20deal%20that%20endangers%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VFX%20is%20rudimentary%20and%20the%20CGI%20creature%2C%20an%20impish%2C%20Gremlin-like%20being%20who%20prances%20around%20at%20will%2C%20is%20not%20the%20sort%20of%20device%20that%20can%20put%20the%20fear%20of%20God%20in%20the%20audience.%20Munjya%2C%20visible%20only%20to%20Bittu%2C%20refuses%20to%20set%20the%20boy%20free%20until%20his%20bidding%20is%20done.%20That%20spells%20trouble%20as%20much%20for%20Bittu%20as%20for%20the%20film.%20The%20creature%20hops%20from%20one%20form%20to%20another%20and%20so%20does%20the%20film.%20Munjya%20never%20quite%20discovers%20a%20solid%20core.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThunder%2C%20lightning%2C%20sea%20waves%2C%20ominous%20shadows%20in%20the%20forest%20and%20a%20tree%20with%20a%20tentacled%20trunk%20are%20all%20pressed%20into%20service%20to%20rustle%20up%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20mystery%20and%20anxiety.%20But%20at%20no%20point%20does%20%3Ci%3EMunjya%3C%2Fi%3E%20manage%20to%20inveigle%20the%20audience%20into%20buying%20into%20the%20wild%20and%20wayward%20yarn%20that%20it%20spins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20the%20prowling%20CGI%20creature%20nor%20the%20boy%20that%20it%20torments%20evoke%20either%20fear%2C%20alarm%20or%20empathy.%20Yes%2C%20an%20attempt%20is%20made%20to%20give%20Bittu%20a%20cherubic%20Harry%20Potter-like%20look%20-%20he%20is%20a%20guy%20who%20must%20dig%20deep%20within%20to%20find%20the%20magic%20that%20could%20help%20him%20counter%20the%20persistent%20%3Ci%3EMunjya%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBittu%20never%20loses%20his%20eyeglasses%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20falls%20he%20endures.%20He%20even%20sleeps%20with%20his%20spectacles%20on.%20We%20do%20want%20him%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20trouble%20he%20is%20but%20way%20more%20interesting%20than%20the%20harried%20boy%20is%20his%20Sikh%20friend%20and%20confidant%20Diljit%20Singh%20Dhillon%20%26quot%3BSpielberg%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20videographer%20who%20aspires%20to%20be%20a%20filmmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20in%20the%20film%2C%20a%20charlatan%2C%20Elvis%20Karim%20Prabhakar%2C%20comes%20in%20with%20his%20'hand%20of%20god'%20to%20exorcise%20ghosts.%20Bittu%20and%20his%20pal%20see%20him%20peddle%20his%20miracle.%20They%20seek%20his%20help%20in%20fighting%20off%20%3Ci%3EMunjya%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20battle%20shifts%20back%20to%20the%20forest%20where%20it%20all%20began.%20From%20there%20on%2C%20it%20is%20a%20free%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FqGb5aKEYR8Q%3Fsi%3D8SJlN61gtKqty__K%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EMunjya%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20shot%20with%20great%20flair%