0to%20consider%20for%20solar%20panel%20installation%20for%20apartments%20and%20rentals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFirstly%2C%20look%20for%20organisations%20like%20Tata%20Power%2C%20Kosher%2C%20and%20Havells%20who%20will%20provide%20technical%20support%20and%20customer%20care%20services%20to%20guide%20and%20counsel%20you%20on%20the%20installation%20and%20financing%20of%20the%20panels.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConduct%20shadow%20analysis%20to%20assess%20how%20much%20solar%20energy%20can%20be%20captured%20in%20a%20specific%20place%20by%20checking%20how%20objects%20like%20trees%20and%20towers%20affect%20the%20solar%20setup.%20It%20takes%20about%203%20to%206%20months%20to%20conduct%20shadow%20analysis.%20The%20installation%20company%20comes%20every%20week%20to%20check%20the%20shadow%20and%20the%20sunlight%20being%20received%20in%20order%20to%20finalise%20the%20panel%20location%20before%20the%20infrastructure%20installation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20family%20of%20five%20living%20in%20a%202BHK%20can%20choose%20to%20install%202%20kW%20for%20100%20percent%20dependency%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344429%2Fsolar-square-rooftop-panel-installation-iit-bombay-grads-neeraj-jain-shreya-mishra-nikhil-nahar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20and%20is%20ideal%20for%20properties%20with%20space%20constraints.%20It%20should%20suffice%20energy%20requirements%20for%20using%20two%20air%20conditioners%2C%20five%20lights%2C%20and%20fans.%20The%20cost%20of%20solar%20panel%20installation%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20Rs%201%20lakh%20and%20it%20takes%20between%2015%20to%2045%20days%20for%20installation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3