ng%5C%22%3E4.%20Nagendra%20Naidu%20Dharmavarapu%20following%20his%20dad%E2%80%99s%20footsteps%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Nagendra%20Naidu%20Dharmavarapu%2C%20one%20thing%20that%20he%20was%20sure%20about%20was%20that%20he%20will%20one%20day%20switch%20to%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CI%20know%20that%20there%20is%20a%20certain%20perspective%20towards%20taking%20up%20farming.%20But%20I%20was%20very%20sure%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20career%20that%20I%20would%20end%20up%20in%20the%20agriculture%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nagendra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20he%20lived%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20problems%20that%20the%20farmers%20faced.%20Even%20when%20he%20was%20pursuing%20his%20engineering%20degree%2C%20he%20would%20return%20often%20to%20his%20family%20farms%20and%20work%20with%20his%20father.%20After%20working%20for%20a%20few%20years%20developing%20startups%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20become%20an%20agri-preneur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20Farmties%20India%20Private%20Limited%20and%20started%20growing%20yellow%20dates%20at%20his%20ancestral%20farm.%20Today%2C%20he%20makes%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20per%20acre%20in%20profits%20selling%20yellow%20dates.%20While%20he%20started%20with%20just%2020%20acres%20of%20farming%20land%20is%20now%20an%20empire%20of%20more%20than%201%2C400%20acres%20of%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Alankrutha%20Chandra%20and%20Meher%20Gundavarum%E2%80%99s%20toxin-free%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20the%20US%20Alankrutha%20Chandra%20and%20Meher%20Gundavarum%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331903%2Fhyderabad-sustainable-brand-ex-techies-quit-jobs-eco-friendly-living-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20a%20toxin-free%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20struck%2C%20the%20couple